- This one when it goes just for
a second, it just kind of like,

00:12:19.963 --> 00:12:22.630 align:middle line:84%
I don't know how to describe it,
except for just suddenly having

00:12:22.630 --> 00:12:25.300 align:middle line:90%
your brain being distracted.

00:12:25.300 --> 00:12:29.640 align:middle line:84%
Just very momentarily, and
then OK, go back to OK,

00:12:29.640 --> 00:12:30.640 align:middle line:90%
that's what I was doing.

00:12:30.640 --> 00:12:32.500 align:middle line:90%
That's what I was thinking.

00:12:32.500 --> 00:12:35.110 align:middle line:84%
I'm trying to think, it's hard
to even describe the sensation.

00:12:35.110 --> 00:12:38.290 align:middle line:84%
- It was quite unusual
to see activations only

00:12:38.290 --> 00:12:39.670 align:middle line:90%
in the left hemisphere.

