lead for each line.

00:18:09.290 --> 00:18:10.580 align:middle line:90%
And it has to be flawless.

00:18:10.580 --> 00:18:11.650 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Geez.

00:18:11.650 --> 00:18:13.150 align:middle line:84%
>>PADGETT: So it's
also the rainbow.

00:18:13.150 --> 00:18:15.580 align:middle line:84%
When you see a double rainbow,
that ring that you see,

00:18:15.580 --> 00:18:16.908 align:middle line:90%
