00:19:35.973 --> 00:19:37.390 align:middle line:84%
>>PADGETT: Not
under a microscope.

00:19:37.390 --> 00:19:37.570 align:middle line:90%
No.

00:19:37.570 --> 00:19:40.000 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: I mean, in terms
of them looking at you

00:19:40.000 --> 00:19:42.820 align:middle line:84%
