00:20:13.210 --> 00:20:16.720 align:middle line:84%
Whereas when we go and we
learn derivatives and integrals

00:20:16.720 --> 00:20:19.510 align:middle line:84%
and calculus and you're
just crunching numbers,

00:20:19.510 --> 00:20:24.160 align:middle line:84%
it's very hard for the students
