applies in the real world,

00:20:28.810 --> 00:20:30.820 align:middle line:84%
and what it is that
it's describing.

00:20:30.820 --> 00:20:32.950 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Have your
savant abilities

00:20:32.950 --> 00:20:36.920 align:middle line:84%
