00:42:58.755 --> 00:43:00.480 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: If you
turn the clock back,

00:43:00.480 --> 00:43:02.670 align:middle line:84%
would you want this to
happen to you again?

00:43:02.670 --> 00:43:04.890 align:middle line:84%
>>PADGETT: I would not
change this for the world.

00:43:04.890 --> 00:43:07.258 align:middle line:84%
It was in the long
run by far the best

00:43:07.258 --> 00:43:08.550 align:middle line:90%
thing that ever happened to me.

00:43:08.550 --> 00:43:09.120 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Really?

00:43:09.120 --> 00:43:10.037 align:middle line:90%
>>PADGETT: Absolutely.

00:43:10.037 --> 00:43:11.280 align:middle line:90%
I met my wife because of it.

00:43:11.280 --> 00:43:12.360 align:middle line:90%
My children exist.

00:43:12.360 --> 00:43:13.980 align:middle line:84%
If I hadn't gotten mugged,
I wouldn't have met my wife.

00:43:13.980 --> 00:43:15.210 align:middle line:90%
My kids wouldn't be here.

00:43:15.210 --> 00:43:19.050 align:middle line:84%
I wouldn't have this
newfound love and fascination

00:43:19.050 --> 00:43:21.840 align:middle line:84%
for the world that I
didn't have before.

00:43:21.840 --> 00:43:25.980 align:middle line:84%
My life has changed so
much, and so much of it now

00:43:25.980 --> 00:43:29.802 align:middle line:84%
is for the better than that
the negatives are unimportant.

00:43:29.802 --> 00:43:31.260 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: And you
found forgiveness.

00:43:31.260 --> 00:43:32.710 align:middle line:90%
>>PADGETT: Absolutely.

00:43:32.710 --> 00:43:35.492 align:middle line:84%
I was surprised, because for
years, I hated those guys.

00:43:35.492 --> 00:43:37.950 align:middle line:84%
I mean, I must have killed them
in my head a million times.

00:43:37.950 --> 00:43:38.460 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Who would blame you?

00:43:38.460 --> 00:43:38.970 align:middle line:90%
>>PADGETT: Right.

00:43:38.970 --> 00:43:40.797 align:middle line:84%
It was like I had so
much anger and I've

00:43:40.797 --> 00:43:41.880 align:middle line:90%
gone through so much pain.

00:43:41.880 --> 00:43:45.720 align:middle line:84%
But when he contacted me,
it just like melted away.

00:43:45.720 --> 00:43:48.552 align:middle line:84%
I realized that he
had a rough life.

00:43:48.552 --> 00:43:50.760 align:middle line:84%
And when I heard about what
had happened to him right

00:43:50.760 --> 00:43:53.040 align:middle line:84%
before that and that he
had turned his life around,

00:43:53.040 --> 00:43:54.690 align:middle line:84%
and he turned his
life around not

00:43:54.690 --> 00:43:56.085 align:middle line:90%
because he felt obligated to.

00:43:56.085 --> 00:43:57.960 align:middle line:84%
He turned his life around
before he found out

00:43:57.960 --> 00:43:59.335 align:middle line:84%
anything that had
happened to me,

00:43:59.335 --> 00:44:01.410 align:middle line:84%
because he wanted to
be a better person.

00:44:01.410 --> 00:44:02.820 align:middle line:90%
And I can understand that.

00:44:02.820 --> 00:44:05.865 align:middle line:90%
I was a silly teenager.

00:44:05.865 --> 00:44:09.240 align:middle line:84%
And I can remember some of the
stupid things that I thought.

00:44:09.240 --> 00:44:11.027 align:middle line:90%
And he completely changed.

00:44:11.027 --> 00:44:13.110 align:middle line:84%
