being on Beyond Belief.

00:44:13.110 --> 00:44:13.530 align:middle line:90%
>>PADGETT: Thank you.

00:44:13.530 --> 00:44:15.210 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: You're a
fascinating individual.

00:44:15.210 --> 00:44:16.210 align:middle line:90%
>>PADGETT: I enjoyed it.

00:44:16.210 --> 00:44:18.420 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: And I wish you all
the success in the world.

00:44:18.420 --> 00:44:18.990 align:middle line:90%
>>PADGETT: Thank you.

